{"tid":2212632,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙控(00005.HK)醜聞後內部指示暫停更新社交媒體","createTime":"2020-09-22T03:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T05:04:01.000Z","uid":78046,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a1e15bbbc69fb566d9ad35de39b70033184528","tid":2212632,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"滙豐控股(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=80d9dcbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)遭洩漏的美國財政部機密文件顯示，過去於懷疑資金來源有問題的情況下，仍為客戶進行交易。相關報道刊出後，外電引述滙控內部文件指，集團國際商業及投資銀行分部市場部主管Tricia Weener週一(21日)向員工指示，至倫敦時間週二(22日)早上11時為止暫停於社交媒體發文，以避免公眾有負面反應，解答零售銀行客戶對業務的問題除外。<br />\n<br />\n滙控發言人拒就報道作出評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1ae0822ba672c1e7ddec8c3029103a6ab2b9e3","tid":2212632,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"真喺要執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb643b3130f5c2930d718b81e32d0fa08541f3fd","tid":2212632,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d72b1674be06125d0cf3fd4471de4aac9e0d874","tid":2212632,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"要收聲 維穩了"},{"pid":"449bb487cda1b9a049f58b2d3a1cd42455b78423","tid":2212632,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"驚閪"},{"pid":"dadcb0711f49e56a1c8cc3f15dcfd89a41c6e8b0","tid":2212632,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"我有筆錢 點黎你唔好知數目都幾大吓 幫我轉去非洲ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /